data.description:
Welcome to 22 Daphne Drive, a move-in ready South Asheville home with a delightful open floor plan. This charming house features three bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, offering plenty of space for comfortable living. The primary suite is conveniently located on the main level, while two additional bedrooms and another full bath are upstairs. With a spacious garage and a private fenced backyard, you'll have ample room for storage and outdoor activities.

Situated in the sought-after Waightstill Mountain neighborhood, enjoy easy access to I-26, Biltmore Park, Bent Creek trails, and the scenic Blue Ridge Parkway. The home boasts new appliances, a low-maintenance exterior, and a hassle-free lifestyle.

As a resident of Waightstill Mountain, you'll have access to the neighborhood's outdoor pool and walking trails for a minimal HOA fee. Don't miss out on this meticulously cared-for home in an excellent location. Schedule your showing today!
